<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,365 --> 00:00:32,300
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,368 --> 00:00:36,168
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,573 --> 00:00:43,411
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,646 --> 00:00:50,711
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:51,020 --> 00:00:57,152
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,293 --> 00:01:01,559
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,631 --> 00:01:05,226
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,301 --> 00:01:08,634
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,705 --> 00:01:12,334
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,408 --> 00:01:16,003
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:19,571
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,649 --> 00:01:23,107
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:27,415
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:39,446 --> 00:01:45,351
<i>Tsunade's Warning.</i>
<i>Ninja No More!</i>

21
00:01:58,565 --> 00:02:01,056
Good work, Akamaru!
You nailed it!

22
00:02:01,268 --> 00:02:03,463
Midair Dynamic Marking!

23
00:02:04,738 --> 00:02:06,569
Next, three twists!

24
00:02:06,874 --> 00:02:08,000
Aim carefully!

25
00:02:14,615 --> 00:02:18,711
Can one call that a walk?
No, I don't think one can.

26
00:02:19,853 --> 00:02:22,253
I can't gather insects at ease.

27
00:02:24,291 --> 00:02:25,622
It's so great...

28
00:02:25,993 --> 00:02:29,451
that the three of you have things
you're good at and that you love...

29
00:02:30,597 --> 00:02:32,189
I hope you'll find
something like that too, Hinata.

30
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,424
You're right...

31
00:02:35,602 --> 00:02:37,035
And, what is it?

32
00:02:38,839 --> 00:02:39,999
You had something
to tell me, didn't you?

33
00:02:40,841 --> 00:02:41,739
Umm...

34
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:43,808
Yeah...

35
00:02:46,113 --> 00:02:47,808
So, using that as a hint,

36
00:02:48,048 --> 00:02:51,484
think about the fastest way
to get to the destination.

37
00:02:52,586 --> 00:02:53,575
Start!

38
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,164
Everyone!

39
00:03:07,634 --> 00:03:10,694
I'm sorry this happens all the time,
but class is over for today.

40
00:03:11,004 --> 00:03:11,902
Yippee!

41
00:03:11,972 --> 00:03:13,769
- Why?
- Huh? Not again.

42
00:03:13,841 --> 00:03:15,502
The handout is your homework!

43
00:03:15,576 --> 00:03:17,100
- What?!
- Huh?!

44
00:03:22,182 --> 00:03:25,276
I'm so happy we didn't have
the class for Taijutsu.

45
00:03:25,452 --> 00:03:29,388
But these days,
class either finishes in the morning

46
00:03:29,456 --> 00:03:31,253
or we have the whole day off...

47
00:03:31,892 --> 00:03:34,156
I wonder if that's really okay.

48
00:03:34,461 --> 00:03:36,292
What's up with acting like
a serious student?

49
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:38,193
Right, Konohamaru?

50
00:03:38,899 --> 00:03:39,695
Huh?

51
00:03:45,572 --> 00:03:46,903
Konohamaru?

52
00:03:59,486 --> 00:04:00,953
Konohamaru!

53
00:04:06,326 --> 00:04:08,954
What do you think you're doing
with Grandpa's things?!

54
00:04:10,564 --> 00:04:11,826
Honorable grandson...

55
00:04:12,733 --> 00:04:14,223
Those belong to my Grandpa!

56
00:04:14,501 --> 00:04:16,196
Where are you taking them?!

57
00:04:16,703 --> 00:04:19,035
Uh... you mean these?

58
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:21,874
They are no longer used,

59
00:04:21,942 --> 00:04:24,410
so I thought I'd put them into storage
in a different location.

60
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:27,144
No longer used, you say...

61
00:04:27,781 --> 00:04:30,944
You think it's okay to take Grandpa's
things away without permission?!

62
00:04:31,218 --> 00:04:34,312
The Fifth Hokage will be using
the chambers, you know.

63
00:04:35,155 --> 00:04:36,213
The Fifth Hokage?

64
00:04:36,957 --> 00:04:38,390
Y-Yes.

65
00:04:39,126 --> 00:04:41,594
The next Hokage
has finally been decided.

66
00:04:42,362 --> 00:04:44,227
The village can have peace of mind now.

67
00:04:45,866 --> 00:04:48,460
That person apparently
doesn't smoke tobacco...

68
00:04:49,736 --> 00:04:51,203
What do you mean, Fifth Hokage?!

69
00:04:51,472 --> 00:04:53,099
It's too soon for that!

70
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:56,302
When you depended on
the Old Man up to recently!

71
00:05:04,985 --> 00:05:07,010
What a lovely fragrance...

72
00:05:10,257 --> 00:05:11,087
Huh?!

73
00:05:12,192 --> 00:05:14,490
Wh-What are you doing?!

74
00:05:14,728 --> 00:05:17,219
That's exactly my question for you!

75
00:05:17,498 --> 00:05:19,022
You perverted kid...

76
00:05:21,068 --> 00:05:22,558
I dare you to say that again!

77
00:05:22,903 --> 00:05:26,361
Huh? You want me
to say it again?

78
00:05:27,074 --> 00:05:29,542
Per-vert-ed kid!

79
00:05:29,643 --> 00:05:31,838
Don't call me that!

80
00:05:31,912 --> 00:05:32,879
Lady Tsunade!

81
00:05:35,482 --> 00:05:38,713
The elders are all waiting,
so we had better hurry.

82
00:05:42,189 --> 00:05:43,918
Yes, I know.

83
00:05:47,094 --> 00:05:49,494
Be careful, little boy.

84
00:05:49,897 --> 00:05:51,956
Please be more conscious
of your actions.

85
00:05:52,032 --> 00:05:54,557
I'm the person
who has to deal with the complaints...

86
00:05:54,902 --> 00:05:55,869
Okay, okay.

87
00:05:58,772 --> 00:06:00,933
I'm not a little boy!

88
00:06:07,047 --> 00:06:08,742
Who the heck are you?!

89
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:11,415
That's my question...

90
00:06:11,485 --> 00:06:12,952
Naruto!

91
00:06:14,254 --> 00:06:15,881
Konohamaru?

92
00:06:16,757 --> 00:06:18,725
Long time no see!

93
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:23,420
Hey, more importantly, have you seen
a big boobed, scary old lady...

94
00:06:23,530 --> 00:06:25,521
I mean, young lady?

95
00:06:26,333 --> 00:06:27,800
I <i>did</i> see her!

96
00:06:28,402 --> 00:06:29,630
- Where did she go?!
- Who the heck is she?!

97
00:06:31,772 --> 00:06:32,864
Who is she?

98
00:06:36,643 --> 00:06:40,010
She has to go
to the hospital straightaway!

99
00:06:40,681 --> 00:06:41,682
Hospital?

100
00:06:41,682 --> 00:06:43,240
That lady may not look it,

101
00:06:43,317 --> 00:06:44,909
but she's an awesome
Medical Corps Ninja!

102
00:06:45,385 --> 00:06:48,320
She finally came back to the village
to become the Hokage, so...

103
00:06:48,589 --> 00:06:51,114
what is she taking her sweet time for?!

104
00:06:51,692 --> 00:06:52,659
Hokage...

105
00:06:53,226 --> 00:06:54,955
The Fifth Hokage.

106
00:06:57,397 --> 00:07:01,026
She better do what
she promised to do.

107
00:07:02,469 --> 00:07:03,401
You're lying...

108
00:07:03,470 --> 00:07:04,198
Huh?

109
00:07:04,738 --> 00:07:05,932
I don't believe you!

110
00:07:06,306 --> 00:07:07,773
It's a lie!

111
00:07:09,977 --> 00:07:10,773
What?

112
00:07:41,208 --> 00:07:45,668
<i>There are seven birds within 50 meters</i>
<i>behind me in the direction of the "2."</i>

113
00:07:49,349 --> 00:07:50,213
Tenten...?

114
00:07:51,051 --> 00:07:52,040
Neji!

115
00:07:56,056 --> 00:07:58,581
I just heard that that Lady Tsunade
has returned!

116
00:07:59,059 --> 00:08:01,653
It's the real McCoy.
Wanna go see her?

117
00:08:03,463 --> 00:08:04,452
Sorry.

118
00:08:05,432 --> 00:08:06,524
But I'm not interested.

119
00:08:07,334 --> 00:08:08,164
Huh?

120
00:08:10,237 --> 00:08:11,329
<i>So there were...</i>

121
00:08:11,905 --> 00:08:13,236
<i>eight birds, huh...</i>

122
00:08:14,841 --> 00:08:16,240
Listen carefully, Tsunade.

123
00:08:16,309 --> 00:08:18,368
We must call the feudal lords

124
00:08:18,445 --> 00:08:21,778
and announce the fact that
the Fifth Hokage has been chosen.

125
00:08:22,482 --> 00:08:26,714
We will start preparations today
for the inauguration ceremony in the village.

126
00:08:27,187 --> 00:08:30,645
Feudal lords and ceremonies
are just a big pain.

127
00:08:30,824 --> 00:08:31,791
Tsunade!

128
00:08:32,626 --> 00:08:37,893
Yes, yes, I know...
This is also the job of the Hokage.

129
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,959
- Genma!
- Here!

130
00:08:40,033 --> 00:08:41,466
- Aoba!
- Here!

131
00:08:42,602 --> 00:08:43,899
Issue an official notice and

132
00:08:44,171 --> 00:08:47,766
convey this matter to those in the village
within the next few days.

133
00:08:48,842 --> 00:08:50,901
We must introduce the Fifth Hokage.

134
00:08:51,445 --> 00:08:52,605
- Yes, ma'am!
- Yes, ma'am!

135
00:08:58,185 --> 00:08:59,379
I hate you, Grandpa!

136
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:01,754
Why did you have to die?

137
00:09:03,490 --> 00:09:04,684
The Fifth Hokage...

138
00:09:11,098 --> 00:09:13,794
Gimme a break,
my shoulders are so stiff.

139
00:09:14,434 --> 00:09:18,871
I wish I could just down
a nice cup of hot <i>sake</i> and relax.

140
00:09:18,939 --> 00:09:19,837
Lady Tsunade!

141
00:09:19,906 --> 00:09:21,305
Wait a second!

142
00:09:21,641 --> 00:09:22,665
Before you do that,

143
00:09:22,743 --> 00:09:25,109
you have something else you need to do,
Old Lady Tsunade!

144
00:09:26,613 --> 00:09:27,477
What was it?

145
00:09:27,948 --> 00:09:29,381
I told you, didn't I?!

146
00:09:29,449 --> 00:09:32,384
About Kakashi Sensei and
Sasuke and Bushy Brow!

147
00:09:32,853 --> 00:09:34,787
Oh... right, right.

148
00:09:35,789 --> 00:09:37,552
Hey, if it isn't Naruto!

149
00:09:37,624 --> 00:09:40,092
Huh? Shikamaru?

150
00:09:40,527 --> 00:09:43,121
Why are you in a place like this?

151
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:44,454
That's my question-

152
00:09:44,531 --> 00:09:46,556
Why are you in a place like this?

153
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,724
I have no idea why,

154
00:09:48,802 --> 00:09:50,633
but my father told me
to come along with him.

155
00:09:51,805 --> 00:09:53,272
What's up with that?

156
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:56,240
Long time no see, Lady Tsunade.

157
00:09:56,610 --> 00:09:59,010
Oh, the kid from the Nara Family, huh.

158
00:09:59,379 --> 00:10:01,313
Are you taking proper care
of the deer?

159
00:10:01,648 --> 00:10:04,549
The antlers of the deer from
that area make very good medicine.

160
00:10:04,618 --> 00:10:06,347
Yes, I'm somehow managing.

161
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:08,578
Hey, Naruto, who's that person

162
00:10:08,655 --> 00:10:10,919
who acts like such
a big shot when she's so young?

163
00:10:11,158 --> 00:10:13,092
That's apparently the new Hokage.

164
00:10:13,293 --> 00:10:13,952
Huh?!

165
00:10:14,928 --> 00:10:17,920
Despite her appearance,
she's an old lady in her fifties.

166
00:10:17,998 --> 00:10:18,794
Yikes!

167
00:10:19,299 --> 00:10:21,199
Well, see you again sometime.

168
00:10:21,501 --> 00:10:22,331
Yes, ma'am.

169
00:10:22,402 --> 00:10:24,370
All right, to the hospital!

170
00:10:24,671 --> 00:10:26,969
See you later, Shikamaru.

171
00:10:27,374 --> 00:10:30,138
I'm will show you an awesome
new technique I learned!

172
00:10:30,777 --> 00:10:32,677
That's the new Fifth Hokage...?

173
00:10:33,246 --> 00:10:35,180
Hey, Shikamaru.

174
00:10:35,882 --> 00:10:40,410
That person is the strongest
and most beautiful person in the world.

175
00:10:40,754 --> 00:10:41,550
Huh?

176
00:10:42,163 --> 00:10:46,429
I mean, she's the one female
amongst the Legendary Sannin.

177
00:10:48,128 --> 00:10:49,925
Huh... A female Hokage!?

178
00:10:50,697 --> 00:10:54,030
I'm not very comfortable with women...

179
00:10:54,534 --> 00:10:55,523
Huh?

180
00:10:55,869 --> 00:10:59,737
Even though they're unusually frank,
they always hang around and

181
00:10:59,806 --> 00:11:03,674
you're never quite sure
whose side they're on.

182
00:11:05,145 --> 00:11:08,808
They always think they can make
men do whatever they want.

183
00:11:09,683 --> 00:11:11,674
Anyway, they're just a pain.

184
00:11:14,321 --> 00:11:15,788
Hey Shikamaru...

185
00:11:16,289 --> 00:11:19,349
Without women,
men wouldn't be born.

186
00:11:20,727 --> 00:11:24,561
If women weren't around,
nothing good would come of men.

187
00:11:25,599 --> 00:11:27,658
No matter how hard-edged
a woman might be,

188
00:11:27,868 --> 00:11:30,564
she'll show her gentle side
to the man she loves.

189
00:11:31,404 --> 00:11:34,498
<i>I can't believe that Pa's saying that...</i>

190
00:11:34,574 --> 00:11:36,599
<i>when he's tied to Mom's apron strings.</i>

191
00:11:38,778 --> 00:11:41,269
You'll understand once
you reach that age.

192
00:11:42,082 --> 00:11:43,481
Oh no!

193
00:11:43,884 --> 00:11:45,875
Let's hurry up and
get our business done...

194
00:11:46,353 --> 00:11:49,117
because Mom will chew us out
if we're late.

195
00:11:49,589 --> 00:11:51,318
Hurry up, Shikamaru!

196
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:54,590
Looks like nothing will come
of some men

197
00:11:54,661 --> 00:11:56,959
even if they have a woman.

198
00:11:58,167 --> 00:12:01,694
Konoha Hospital

199
00:12:06,241 --> 00:12:07,230
I'm coming in.

200
00:12:09,511 --> 00:12:10,569
Who are you...?

201
00:12:15,250 --> 00:12:16,444
<i>What a beautiful woman...</i>

202
00:12:17,352 --> 00:12:19,013
Sakura, Sakura!

203
00:12:19,087 --> 00:12:20,577
Everything will be all right now!

204
00:12:21,056 --> 00:12:22,489
I brought along an awesome person.

205
00:12:24,459 --> 00:12:26,484
Sasuke will be fine now!

206
00:12:28,096 --> 00:12:29,063
Naruto...

207
00:12:33,068 --> 00:12:36,094
<i>Those two flowers aren't from</i>
<i>the same day.</i>

208
00:12:36,972 --> 00:12:39,202
<i>So this kid is coming here</i>
<i>every day, huh...</i>

209
00:12:40,442 --> 00:12:42,774
I heard from Guy Sensei...

210
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:45,544
Please save Sasuke.

211
00:12:46,415 --> 00:12:48,542
OK, leave it to me.

212
00:13:27,155 --> 00:13:28,019
Sasuke!

213
00:13:28,557 --> 00:13:29,489
Sasuke...

214
00:13:39,902 --> 00:13:41,130
Sasuke!

215
00:13:42,604 --> 00:13:44,037
Sasuke, you...!

216
00:14:11,767 --> 00:14:16,101
<i>Hmm, despite his appearance,</i>
<i>that Naruto is pretty considerate.</i>

217
00:14:16,738 --> 00:14:17,432
Huh?

218
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:19,064
Next! Next!

219
00:14:22,110 --> 00:14:24,044
How disgraceful!

220
00:14:25,514 --> 00:14:28,540
To be taken down by
just two insurgents.

221
00:14:29,851 --> 00:14:32,411
And here I thought you were a genius.

222
00:14:34,389 --> 00:14:35,321
I'm sorry...

223
00:14:36,291 --> 00:14:38,816
All right! Kakashi Sensei's done!

224
00:14:38,927 --> 00:14:40,417
Next, Bushy Brow!

225
00:14:40,762 --> 00:14:43,253
Please hurry up and
take a look at my disciple Lee!

226
00:14:46,568 --> 00:14:47,466
Lee!

227
00:14:49,204 --> 00:14:51,434
I brought Lady Tsunade here!

228
00:15:02,918 --> 00:15:04,476
That's your disciple?

229
00:15:04,786 --> 00:15:08,187
Yes! My beloved, beloved disciple!

230
00:15:09,591 --> 00:15:10,387
I see...

231
00:15:12,661 --> 00:15:13,457
Naruto.

232
00:15:13,528 --> 00:15:14,290
Huh?

233
00:15:14,730 --> 00:15:17,358
Is it really okay for you
to be idling away your time here like this?

234
00:15:17,432 --> 00:15:18,831
Uh, I almost forgot!

235
00:15:18,934 --> 00:15:21,664
I had an appointment to
meet Iruka Sensei!

236
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:23,128
Go on!

237
00:15:23,205 --> 00:15:25,867
OK! I'll leave the rest in your hands!

238
00:15:26,141 --> 00:15:26,800
All right!

239
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,107
Hey, Naruto!

240
00:15:33,181 --> 00:15:35,081
You're late, Iruka Sensei!

241
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,447
Sorry, sorry.

242
00:15:36,518 --> 00:15:39,248
There were lots of things to do
with respect to the Fifth Hokage.

243
00:15:39,521 --> 00:15:41,045
I guess...

244
00:15:45,627 --> 00:15:46,651
Thanks for waiting!

245
00:15:46,995 --> 00:15:48,656
I'm digging in!

246
00:15:52,534 --> 00:15:53,558
Naruto.

247
00:15:53,635 --> 00:15:54,363
Huh?

248
00:15:55,070 --> 00:15:59,234
You have really developed compared
to the time when you wanted this.

249
00:15:59,307 --> 00:16:00,399
I have, haven't I?

250
00:16:00,575 --> 00:16:02,338
You think so too, right?

251
00:16:02,878 --> 00:16:05,312
This headband that I received
from Iruka Sensei

252
00:16:05,547 --> 00:16:07,879
suits me perfectly, don't you think?

253
00:16:10,819 --> 00:16:12,480
Stop being so cocky!

254
00:16:12,621 --> 00:16:14,714
You still have a long,
long way to go!

255
00:16:14,956 --> 00:16:16,947
You have lots of work to do!

256
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:19,957
Listen carefully, Naruto!

257
00:16:21,029 --> 00:16:23,156
The Leaf Village is in
a very difficult situation right now.

258
00:16:23,832 --> 00:16:27,859
Starting with the Third Hokage,
we lost many fine Shinobi.

259
00:16:28,103 --> 00:16:30,867
The current strength of the Leaf
is less than half what it normally is.

260
00:16:31,473 --> 00:16:33,771
Despite that, we must continue
to carry out our missions.

261
00:16:33,975 --> 00:16:35,306
Why is that?

262
00:16:35,377 --> 00:16:37,311
If you don't have enough manpower,
you should turn it down.

263
00:16:37,479 --> 00:16:38,969
No, that won't do...

264
00:16:39,614 --> 00:16:41,047
If we turn down our missions,

265
00:16:41,116 --> 00:16:44,210
it would be like announcing
to other countries our weakened state.

266
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:48,578
Even Kakashi Sensei who is still ailing
will probably be assigned to missions.

267
00:16:49,424 --> 00:16:52,188
I see... these are difficult times.

268
00:16:53,395 --> 00:16:55,590
Hey! This concerns you too!

269
00:16:55,931 --> 00:16:58,627
You need to play an active role
and carry out your duties

270
00:16:58,700 --> 00:16:59,997
in order to aid Lady Tsunade.

271
00:17:00,068 --> 00:17:00,659
Yeah.

272
00:17:01,002 --> 00:17:03,994
But, before I do that,
I need to satisfy my stomach.

273
00:17:07,075 --> 00:17:08,804
That's just like you.

274
00:17:12,881 --> 00:17:14,075
Do your best!

275
00:17:17,786 --> 00:17:18,844
Seconds!

276
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:20,649
Hey, hey!
How'd you finish so fast?!

277
00:17:25,927 --> 00:17:27,394
I'll be straight with you.

278
00:17:28,430 --> 00:17:29,988
Give up being a Shinobi.

279
00:17:42,310 --> 00:17:47,270
L-Lady Tsunade...
don't joke like that.

280
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:52,680
There are numerous bone fragments
in the area around important nerves.

281
00:17:52,854 --> 00:17:55,254
Moreover, they are deeply embedded.

282
00:17:56,825 --> 00:18:00,386
You're not physically capable
of carrying out the missions of a Shinobi.

283
00:18:02,197 --> 00:18:05,132
Come now, Lady Tsunade,
don't joke like that...

284
00:18:05,567 --> 00:18:07,330
Even if I were to operate...

285
00:18:07,669 --> 00:18:09,068
Don't be fooled, Lee!

286
00:18:09,371 --> 00:18:11,430
That Lady Tsunade is an impostor!

287
00:18:11,907 --> 00:18:14,341
You changed yourself
using the Transformation Jutsu,

288
00:18:14,409 --> 00:18:15,467
you evil woman!

289
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:17,300
Who the heck are you?!

290
00:18:31,459 --> 00:18:34,428
Don't I have any... chance?

291
00:18:36,097 --> 00:18:38,588
There is no one besides me
who is capable of doing the surgery

292
00:18:38,667 --> 00:18:40,294
and it would take too much time.

293
00:18:41,236 --> 00:18:43,431
Furthermore, there is a huge risk...

294
00:18:44,306 --> 00:18:45,204
Risk?

295
00:18:45,807 --> 00:18:49,641
The probability of
a successful surgery is 50% at best,

296
00:18:50,579 --> 00:18:51,705
and if it fails...

297
00:18:53,848 --> 00:18:54,678
You'll die.

298
00:19:07,495 --> 00:19:08,427
<i>Guy Sensei!</i>

299
00:19:08,763 --> 00:19:11,755
<i>I'm not at all ready</i>
<i>to throw in the towel!</i>

300
00:19:14,803 --> 00:19:18,739
<i>Guy Sensei, what's this god awful</i>
<i>bitter rice dumpling?</i>

301
00:19:19,474 --> 00:19:22,409
<i>They are Youthful Vigor Herbal Pills.</i>

302
00:19:22,811 --> 00:19:25,405
<i>If you eat one hundred of them,</i>
<i>they should heal your wound.</i>

303
00:19:26,114 --> 00:19:28,241
<i>I see, if I don't eat</i>
<i>one hundred of them,</i>

304
00:19:28,316 --> 00:19:29,977
<i>my wound won't heal, right?</i>

305
00:19:34,256 --> 00:19:36,520
<i>N-Not in a single day!</i>

306
00:19:37,859 --> 00:19:41,056
It's better that you give up being
a Shinobi and look for a different path.

307
00:19:42,897 --> 00:19:43,761
Lee...

308
00:20:10,525 --> 00:20:11,389
Lee...

309
00:20:32,247 --> 00:20:35,114
If I knew this was going to happen,
I shouldn't have brought you to him.

310
00:20:35,583 --> 00:20:36,515
Don't say that...!

311
00:20:37,952 --> 00:20:42,685
I am painfully aware of how you feel,
but it's better to be clear.

312
00:20:43,692 --> 00:20:46,058
Because it's something he'll have
to understand sooner or later.

313
00:20:47,996 --> 00:20:49,258
The longer we wait...

314
00:20:50,532 --> 00:20:52,796
the harder it will be for him.

315
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:10,279
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

316
00:21:10,352 --> 00:21:14,686
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

317
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:18,817
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

318
00:21:20,061 --> 00:21:24,521
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

319
00:21:24,699 --> 00:21:30,137
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

320
00:21:30,638 --> 00:21:34,938
<i>That hold us together</i>

321
00:21:35,410 --> 00:21:44,648
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

322
00:21:44,719 --> 00:21:47,313
<i>you say laughingly</i>

323
00:21:47,555 --> 00:21:53,221
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

324
00:21:53,795 --> 00:21:58,164
<i>Like a comet,</i>

325
00:21:58,233 --> 00:22:04,331
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

326
00:22:04,406 --> 00:22:11,505
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

327
00:22:12,514 --> 00:22:21,889
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

328
00:22:23,224 --> 00:22:30,756
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

329
00:22:30,832 --> 00:22:34,825
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

330
00:22:37,672 --> 00:22:41,005
Konohamaru, just come out
from there already!

331
00:22:41,075 --> 00:22:41,837
Shut up!

332
00:22:42,110 --> 00:22:44,203
Listen, I'll treat you to
a bowl of ramen!

333
00:22:44,546 --> 00:22:45,410
Don't want any!

334
00:22:45,914 --> 00:22:49,315
OK then. I'll add pork slices and eggs.

335
00:22:49,584 --> 00:22:50,676
You're such a pest!

336
00:22:50,752 --> 00:22:52,344
What did you just say?!

337
00:22:52,754 --> 00:22:55,279
In that case,
I'll pull you out by force!

338
00:22:55,356 --> 00:22:56,789
Be ready for that!

339
00:22:57,559 --> 00:22:59,925
Next time:
"The Will of Fire Still Burns!"

340
00:22:59,994 --> 00:23:01,621
Don't miss it!
